      <title>Clearlake 同意从 Natixis 收购私人信贷管理公司 MV</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/clearlake-agrees-to-buy-private-credit-manager-mv-from-natixis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份声明称，私募市场投资者 Clearlake Capital Group LP 已同意从 Natixis Investment Managers LP 手中收购专注于欧洲的投资公司 MV Credit Partners LLP。]]></description>
